<item>
            <title>[HBASE-9545] NPE when trying to get cluster status on an hbase cluster that isn&apos;t there</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9545</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As part of some fault injection testing, I&apos;m trying to talk to an HBaseCluster that isn&apos;t there, opening a connection and expecting things to fail. It turns out you can create an &lt;tt&gt;HBaseAdmin&lt;/tt&gt; instance, but when you ask for its cluster status the NPE surfaces&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
